@startuml
!theme plain

title UIM SAP Application Autoscaler (AAS) - Executive View

actor "Platform Team" as Team

cloud "Cloud Foundry Apps" as CFApps
cloud "Container Registry" as Registry

node "Kubernetes" {
  component "AAS Service\n(Dlang + vibe.d + UIM)" as AAS
  component "Kubernetes Service + HPA" as K8s
}

Team --> AAS : Define scaling policies
CFApps --> AAS : Send runtime/custom metrics
AAS --> CFApps : Scale in/out decisions
Registry --> AAS : Container image delivery
K8s --> AAS : Runtime orchestration

note bottom of AAS
Outcome:
Automatic, policy-based scaling
for performance and cost efficiency.
end note

@enduml
